<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <title>YouTunnel — Terms</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css"/>
</head>
<body class="login-body">
  <div class="login-bg">
    <div class="login-wrap" style="max-width:600px;">
      <div class="login-logo">
        <div class="logo-icon">⬡</div>
        <h1>YouTunnel</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="terms-box">
        <h2>Terms & Privacy</h2>
        <p>By accessing YouTunnel, you agree to the following:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>All communications within this tunnel are private and confidential.</li>
          <li>You will not share access credentials with unauthorized parties.</li>
          <li>All activity is logged and monitored by the system administrator.</li>
          <li>Unauthorized use or distribution of content is strictly prohibited.</li>
          <li>Your identity and behavior are subject to review by TunnelMaster.</li>
          <li>Accounts found violating these terms may be disabled without notice.</li>
        </ul>
        <form action="/terms/accept" method="POST">
          <button type="submit" class="btn-login" style="margin-top:20px;">I Accept — Enter the Tunnel</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
